generated_description: kaneda is a full-service restaurant located in utsunomiya, tochigi prefecture, specializing in skewered grilled chicken (yakitori). the restaurant offers a variety of skewers made from both seafood and mountain delicacies, fried with a secret blend of flour and served with a secret sauce. kaneda provides seating options including large counter seats, semi-private table seats, and a large tatami room that can accommodate up to 30 people. the restaurant is known for its healthy skewers and creative dishes made with carefully selected fresh ingredients. kaneda caters to various occasions, including business meetings, parties, and special events, and offers a range of menus, including a special ham burger made with domestic black-bellied wagyu beef, a daily smoothie, and a vegetable biryani. the restaurant is designed with a modern japanese style and is accessible with parking available.
